Hexosamine pathway metabolites enhance protein quality control and prolong life.

Denzel MS(1), Storm NJ(1), Gutschmidt A(2), Baddi R(1), Hinze Y(1), Jarosch 
E(3), Sommer T(4), Hoppe T(2), Antebi A(5).

